  "firstAcquaintance": "A wanderer dressed in strange attire, highly guarded, possessing unique powers but absolutely refusing to use them.",
  "personality": "Depressed and always sullen, she chooses to simply endure whatever comes her way.",
  "like": "Stamps, trendy trinkets",
  "familiarData": "Born in an information age where the internet was already well-developed, she was loved by her parents and happily spent each day with family and friends.\nOne day, Huanghuxi and her entire class were transported to another world, where many gained powerful special abilities. Hearing that humans in this world were enslaved by demons, they decided to help liberate the slaves.\nHowever, the Demon Lord appeared.\nThe special abilities they gained upon crossing over, the knowledge advanced beyond this world -- all became empty talk before the Demon Lord, who slaughtered half the classmates in an instant.\nThe surviving classmates fled, then violently argued over abandoning their peers and facing the Demon Lord, eventually turning on each other.\nWhether by luck or the Demon Lord's disinterest, Huanghuxi escaped the Demon Lord's pursuit, but she was now the only one left from her entire class. Since then, she has never dared to use her special abilities again, surviving precariously in the wilderness as a wanderer...",
